editable

private boolean editable

Is the table column editable? The default value is false. Only if this column is editable method write(Appendable) will write the edit flag!

The flag only belongs to tables. Forms does not known the flag (and ignored because default value is false).

See Also:
parse(String, String), write(Appendable)

hidden

private boolean hidden

Is the table column hidden? The default value is false. Only if this column is hidden method write(Appendable) will write the edit flag!

The flag only belongs to tables. Forms does not known the flag (and ignored because default value is false).

See Also:
parse(String, String), write(Appendable)

Method Detail

parse

public void parse(String _url,
                  String _content)
Parses a field / column. This includes:
  • alt label
  • HRef href
  • range URL
  • update URL
  • label
  • name
  • sortType
  • sortProgram
  • expression
  • isBusinessObject or isRelationship expression
  • users who have access to a field / column
  • scale
  • height and width
  • minimum height and minimum width
  • auto height flag
  • auto width flag
  • edit flag for web tables
  • hidden flag for web tables
  • settings

Parameters:
_url - URL to parse
_content - content of the URL to parse

write

public void write(Appendable _out)
           throws IOException
